      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A$ un anneau commutatif et $I$ un id{\\'e}al de $A$.\n\nOn note $\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq } \\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}$\n(radical de $I$).",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span> un anneau commutatif et\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span> un id<span>é</span>al de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq }\n\\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}\\)</span> (radical de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span>).</p>\n"
